{"tid":872241,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人已經頹到就黎癡線","createTime":"2018-10-22T14:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T15:23:01.000Z","uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a76846f05ea36d185b2510036713a942f201cb85","tid":872241,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n無乜朋友<br />\n日常既朋友同社交都係由工作帶比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔係深厚到可以約出街果種<br />\n<br />\n然後半年無拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐘意果個就只係想我做sp<br />\n正一人渣 食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又要返工返學 返工時間長 返埋學既話<br />\n返到屋企已經十點咁上下<br />\n空檔出黎既時間太概一星期先得一日咁大把<br />\n興趣嗜好又無 目標又無<br />\n屋企人更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩老做生意 好日都唔見<br />\n屋企人都唔會話出街食飯/去旅行<br />\n<br />\n成日都要一個人去旅行<br />\n<br />\n基本上真係乜撚都無<br />\n中學同學就以為我好好景 搵好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n愈黎愈識唔到朋友<br />\n個青春就撚黎燒完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生存會唔會太撚無聊<br />\n<br />\n今日見到人地有手仔拖都好提子<br />\n但未見到有岩既人出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327748a2ea5cb6bc1f685503eac7763adcba4b14","tid":872241,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"好彩我本身都痴線架"},{"pid":"959d3c010a43b82f6f219418819ea1c5afee2df7","tid":872241,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"327748a2ea5cb6bc1f685503eac7763adcba4b14","tid":872241,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"好彩我本身都痴線架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:22:36.000Z","msg":"咁你癡線D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7759afa3de27466040af541b0e73376c7780706e","tid":872241,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislik